/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-02.md:39:### 6. Step 3 uses non-canonical decompositions without fixing a representation
